  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion, garlic, carrots, and celery to the saucepan and cook until the vegetables are softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add cumin, salt, black pepper, and sumac to the saucepan and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add rice to the saucepan and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add pomegranate molasses to the saucepan and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add cottage cheese to the saucepan and cook until the mixture is well combined and heated through, about 2-3 minutes.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving dish and sprinkle with crushed pine nuts, pomegranate seeds, and fresh parsley.",
    "Serve hot with a sprinkle of sumac for extra flavor.",
    "Garnish with additional pomegranate seeds and parsley if desired.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
